snippet.title: Dream Day: Wedding Playthrough
snippet.description:
BEWARE VERY GLITCHY SOUND, ESPECIALLY AT THE END;IT GETS SUDDENLY VERY LOUD!

Blurb: 'A romantic seek-and-find adventure featuring beautiful graphics and unique puzzle games. Visit the florist, gown shop, bakery, and other shops to make Jenny's wedding day a dream! But be warned! The challenging Wedding Crisis levels are sure to throw you for a loop! Can you make Jenny's Dream Day Wedding happen?'

If you'd like to play this game or one like it you can find it on https://www.bigfishgames.com/
